647c6db78148c72b77b697","tid":616840,"uid":70335,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"quote":{"pid":"8b43dc68f03b901cd75b86d55c5c8f9111d08be4","tid":616840,"uid":36077,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"85cc62c0bde3be4f0aa474ac4b02e3045b6c51fe","tid":616840,"uid":70335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T13:32:55.000Z","msg":"有無文獻睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T13:54:00.000Z","msg":"大澳門帝國有萄葡牙睇<br />\n大把人走去避難<br />\nGoogle搵大把"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T14:15:36.000Z","msg":"二戰後，日本在亞洲戰場迅速擴張，逐步威脅到澳門的安全。葡萄牙找到了巴西幫忙。此時的巴西早已獨立，但雙方保持了不錯的關係。如何幫忙？就是請巴西向日本政府發一個外交照會，大意是：如果日本入侵澳門，巴西將遣返所有的日本移民。在300w移民可能對國內造成的巨大壓力面前，經過再三權衡，日本最終放棄了攻占澳門的罪惡念頭。<br />\n<br />\n點解日本仔會咁多人走去巴西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T08:00:38.000Z","msg":"耕田 日本糧食一直唔夠自給自足"},{"pid":"20be45c164dfe29d0c8e747f4e502cf46cbe4c27","tid":616840,"uid":123711,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T08:28:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d4e4b3ff9d2876de4c430bc31210c034fa5c133","tid":616840,"uid":99225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T09:02:49.000Z","msg":"日軍條進軍路線可以比支那參考"},{"pid":"9855eb3468108710f8153076e93108efb9728139","tid":616840,"uid":168903,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"996dad855e19ce7103ddea9f48fece8ff0851f6c","tid":616840,"uid":70293,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T14:01:12.000Z","msg":"連登仔: I Love Japan!!!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T09:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9647c4fa64fb3cd79019b0c076c1ece722b15de","tid":616840,"uid":95,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5f4d4c1575651de682731075848874623603dc7c","tid":616840,"uid":50328,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"3e8a9c38306036d16e647c6db78148c72b77b697","tid":616840